
### Summary

- **HTML:** Provides the structure for the note input area and the notes display area.
- **CSS:** Styles the notes app for a clean and simple user interface.
- **JavaScript:** Contains the logic to handle adding, deleting, and rendering notes, as well as saving them to local storage.

You can further enhance this project by adding features such as editing notes, searching notes, or adding categories or tags to notes. If you need any further assistance or have any questions, feel free to ask!
